\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 February\'a0Campaign\'a0\'96\'a0Tried and Tested\'a0
\f1\fs24 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa106\partightenfactor0

\f0 \cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 Focused on supporting gravel riders\'a0through quality content such as guides and a collection of routes provided by the Ribble Outliers, our internal team and UGC.\'a0This can be achieved easily using Strava and the\'a0routes\'a0embed\'a0feature.\'a0\cb1 \uc0\u8232 \cb3 Underlined with announcements that\'a0demonstrate\'a0our support for pro sports,\'a0events in the\'a0category and supported by a category discount.\'a0
\f1 \cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa106\partightenfactor0

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 \cb3 Who is it aimed at?\'a0
\f1\fs24 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa213\partightenfactor0

\f0 \cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 Male and female gravel riders aged\'a030 to 45\'a0who ride through winter because riding is part of their week. They enjoy\'a0exploring\'a0mixed\'a0terrain\'a0and time outside. They do not\'a0extra\'a0motivation,\'a0they\'92re\'a0the ones that\'a0simply ride.\'a0
\f1 \cb1 \

\f0 \cb3 These riders\'a0might be new to gravel, or already have a gravel bike, but\'a0either way, they\'a0want\'a0something\'a0that feel worth heading out for.\'a0\'a0Good gravel can be hard to find\'a0and as a category\'a0it\'92s\'a0subtly different, so routes\'a0and guides\'a0shared by real riders\'a0are interesting for them.\'a0
\f1 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa213\partightenfactor0

\f0 \cf4 \cb5 ADD RIDER CARICATURE\cb3 \'a0
\f1 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa106\partightenfactor0

\f0\fs29\fsmilli14667 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 What behaviour change do we want?\'a0
\f1\fs24 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa213\partightenfactor0

\f0 \cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 We want riders to see Ribble part of their gravel riding\'a0
\f1 \cb1 \

\f0 \cb3 They should feel that gravel is easy to reach in February, with routes, guidance and support that make the first step simple. This is how we help them\'a0enjoy\'a0the\'a0season ahead\'a0and\'a0keep\'a0Ribble in mind\'a0when they think about where and how they\'a0ride.\'a0It\'a0is about making gravel easier to ride and easier to reach.\'a0
\f1 \cb1 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa106\partightenfactor0

