\pard\pardeftab720\sa106\partightenfactor0

\f0 \cf4 \cb3 This is a\'a0simple statement about riders and the bikes that match their habit.\'a0\'a0
\f1 \cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 \

\f0 \cf4 \cb3 \strokec4 Ribble\'a0is\'a0a good source\'a0for gravel routes and\'a0guides, and\'a0has the bikes to make this possible.\'a0
\f1 \cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa106\partightenfactor0

